OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FDavid Lammy has told JD Vance he was
OL,7,Fwrong to link Henry Nowak's murder to
OL,8,Fimmigration, and he warned the US vice-
OL,9,Fpresident the intervention on social
OL,10,Fmedia was "not helpful".
OL,12,FThe deputy prime minister said he
OL,13,Fchallenged Vance in a "robust" phone
OL,14,Fcall on Saturday after the US
OL,15,Fpolitician appeared to blame the
OL,16,Fkilling on a "mass invasion" of people
OL,17,Finto Europe.
