OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FThe 18-year-old student was handcuffed
OL,7,Fby police who ignored his pleas that
OL,8,Fhe had been stabbed as he lay dying
OL,9,Fafter his British-born killer, Vickrum
OL,10,FDigwa, claimed to have been the victim
OL,11,Fof a racist attack.
OL,13,FLammy, who shares an unlikely
OL,14,Ffriendship with Vance despite their
OL,15,Fdifferent political backgrounds, said
OL,16,Fthe two had disagreed about the
OL,17,Fdetails surrounding the murder.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
