OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780855879
OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FLammy, who is also Justice Secretary,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that the pair spoke on
OL,8,Fthe phone and that he told the vice
OL,9,Fpresident the UK's democratic process
OL,10,Fis "working well".
OL,12,FThe deputy PM said he told JD Vance he
OL,13,Ffundamentally "disagreed" with him
OL,14,Fover the details and causes of the
OL,15,Fcase, "this has got nothing to do with
OL,16,Fmass migration."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
