OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FIn the latest intervention by the
OL,7,FTrump administration over the murder,
OL,8,FVance had said on Friday: "Henry Nowak
OL,9,Fdied the same way a civilisation dies:
OL,10,FAbandoned, handcuffed by authorities
OL,11,Fwho neither trusted nor cared for him,
OL,12,Fand accused of hate crimes he did not
OL,13,Fcommit.
OL,15,F"His murder is as tragic as it is
OL,16,Fenraging.
OL,26,@pD@[OUwD@AOU
