OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,F"He should still be alive today, and
OL,7,Fhe would be if the last few
OL,8,Fgenerations of European elites had
OL,9,Fstood their ground against the
OL,10,Fpolitics of self-hatred and the mass
OL,11,Finvasion of migrants, many of whom
OL,12,Fdespise the West and the people who
OL,13,Flove it."
OL,15,FThe vice-president said the response
OL,16,Fto Nowak's death should be "righteous
OL,17,Fanger", in a post on X that came after
OL,18,Fviolent unrest in Southampton on
OL,19,FTuesday, near the spot where the
OL,20,Fteenager was killed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]xD@\OUyD@FO]
