OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FAsked whether he had given Vance a
OL,7,Fticking-off, Lammy said: "We had an
OL,8,Fagreeable conversation because we have
OL,9,Fgot a relationship, but I wanted to
OL,10,Fmake it clear to him that I disagree
OL,11,Fwith some of the facts that he was
OL,12,Fasserting and to present the facts to
OL,13,Fhim."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUuD@EO]
