OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FHe added: "I also urged him that it's
OL,7,Fnot helpful to tweet in this way,
OL,8,Fpartly because of what the Nowak
OL,9,Ffamily have asked for, and reminded
OL,10,Fhim about their desire not to make
OL,11,Fthis an issue of division and hatred,
OL,12,Fbut to make this an issue of common
OL,13,Fsense."
OL,15,FVance's intervention came after the US
OL,16,FState Department linked "two-tier
OL,17,Fpolicing" to Henry Nowak's death,
OL,18,Fwhich Downing Street has firmly
OL,19,Frejected.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@GO]xD@YOUyD@IO]
