OL,3,CDavid Lammy tells JD Vance he is
OL,4,C'wrong' after Henry Nowak intervention
OL,6,FDigwa was given a life sentence with a
OL,7,Fminimum of 21 years in prison for
OL,8,Fstabbing Nowak with a ceremonial knife
OL,9,Fwith a 21cm blade, which he carried as
OL,10,Fpart of his Sikh religion.
OL,12,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct is investigating Hampshire
OL,14,FPolice's response in Nowak's case.
OL,16,FAttorney General Lord Hermer is also
OL,17,Fconsidering whether to refer the
OL,18,Fkiller's sentencing to the Court of
OL,19,FAppeal under the unduly lenient
OL,20,Fscheme, Lammy confirmed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
